      several trainings and certifications in <b>Data Science</b>, <b
        >Advanced Data Analytics</b
      >, and <b>Project Management</b>, to name a few.
    </p>
    <p>
      Here's my <b
        ><a href="https://linkedin.com/in/alharkan" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a
        ></b
      > profile for a more complete résumé.
    </p>
    <hr />
    <p>
      I watch explanatory &amp; documentary videos a lot —on science,
      technology, business; and I curate those videos in these <b
        ><a
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
