      >.
    </p>
    <p>With that being said, I can help you with:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
      <li>Digital Media Research</li>
      <li>Software &amp; Automation</li>
      <li>Data Analytics &amp; Visualization</li>
      <li>Digital Content Production</li>
      <li>Mobile Videography &amp; Journalism</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Just <b><a href="mailto:alharkan7@gmail.com">hit me up</a></b> or <b
        ><a
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
